<section class="mission-statement">
  <h2>Mission statement</h2>
  <p>Meedan builds web and mobile tools and implements creative projects for journalists and translators. Like our namesake the Arabic town square, our tools serve as a gathering place for talented people working to add context to the social web. Our approach is human-centered, creative, and ambitious. Our partners are a world-class group of media companies, universities, and NGOs. We look to a world where understanding facilitated by global conversation is a bit wider, deeper, and more effective.
  </p>

  <p>To get there, we want to build the best tools and platforms in support of global journalism and translation. We are a team of designers, technologists and journalists who focus on open source investigation of digital media and crowdsourced translation of social media. With our partners, we support research, curriculum development, and new forms of digital storytelling.
  </p>
</section>

